message.subject: Introduction from a mutual connection
message.body:
Hi Sarah,

a mutual connection suggested I reach out to you regarding your work at TechStartup Inc.

I'm the founder of Equitle, an AI-powered platform that's helping private equity firms automate their deal sourcing and due diligence processes. Given your expertise in Technology and your role as VP of Engineering, I thought you might be interested in learning about how we're using AI to transform the investment process.

We've already helped several firms reduce their deal evaluation time by 60% while improving accuracy. I'd love to share some insights about our approach and see if there might be opportunities for collaboration.

Would you be available for a brief call this week?

Best regards,
Shariq Hafizi
Founder & CEO, Equitle

Looking forward to connecting!

message.subject: Quick question about Venture Capital Partners
message.body:
Hi Michael,

I came across your profile and was impressed by your work at Venture Capital Partners as a Investment Director. 
I noticed you have experience with Financial Analysis, Due Diligence, Portfolio Management, which is exactly what we're working on at Equitle.

I'm reaching out because we're building an AI-powered investment platform that helps private equity firms streamline their deal sourcing and due diligence process. Given your background in Finance, I thought you might find our approach interesting.

Would you be open to a brief 15-minute call this week to discuss how we're using AI to revolutionize the investment process?

Best regards,
Shariq Hafizi
Founder & CEO, Equitle

P.S. I'd love to share some insights about how AI is transforming the investment landscape.
